text: Iphigenia is a 1977 Greek drama movie directed by Michael Cacoyannis and starring Irene Papas, Tatiana Papamoschou, Kostas Kazakos, Costas Carras. It was nominated for an Academy Award in 1978. ==Other websites== * * Category:1977 drama movies Category:Greek movies Category:Movies directed by Michael Cacoyannis
